text: Dino Cinieri (born 9 July 1955 in Firminy, Loire) is a member of the National Assembly of France. He represents the Loire department, and is a member of the Republicans. ==References== Category:1955 births Category:Living people Category:People from Firminy Category:French people of Italian descent Category:Rally for the Republic politicians Category:Union for a Popular Movement politicians Category:The Republicans (France) politicians Category:The Social Right Category:Christian Democratic Party (France) politicians Category:Deputies of the 12th National Assembly of the French Fifth Republic Category:Deputies of the 13th National Assembly of the French Fifth Republic Category:Deputies of the 14th National Assembly of the French Fifth Republic Category:Deputies of the 15th National Assembly of the French Fifth Republic Category:Regional councillors of Auvergne-Rhône-Alpes
title: Dino Cinieri
